(6799, NULL, 'Dark Chocolate Ganache 70-30', NULL, 0, 'cut & enrobed', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'mix together and heat up to 40°C.\r\nmelt the chocolate at 35°C\r\nadd at ambient temperature to the chocolate. \r\nthen add everything to a Robot-Coupe and emulsify. \r\nframe at a temperature between 30 and 35°C. \r\nallow to crystallise and cut into 22*22mm pieces\r\ndip into Callebaut chocolate of your choice', NULL, '', 0, 0.999, NULL, 0, 1, 0, 'reel', '2019-01-01 19:12:55', 0, 0, 0, 1, 4.71, 0, '60', 3, 491, '0', 0, '84', '0.84', 491),
