(7126, NULL, 'Pistachio Ganache \"Antep\"', NULL, 0, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'o	Dissolve the sugars and butter into the cream by heating up to 40C\r\no	Add the cinnamon powder and pistachio paste\r\no	Melt the chocolate and cocoa butter at 35C\r\no	Emulsify and preset to a temperature of 30-32C\r\no	Frame\r\no	Allow to crystallize for 24 hours\r\no	Give a base\r\no	Cut and Dip into pre-crystallised milk chocolate\r\n', NULL, '', 0, 1.305, NULL, 0, 1, 0, 'reel', '2019-04-06 21:01:18', 0, 0, 0, 0, 5.77, 0, '1', 3, 491, '0', 0, '97', '0.97', 491),
