(8146, NULL, 'Ganache blanche vanille\r\nVanilla white ganache (copie)', 'Vanilla Ivory Ganache', 0, 'A cadrer et découper\r\nTo frame and cut', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Tiédir la crème à 30°\r\nDans le cutter. placer le chocolat blanc à 32/34°\r\nAjouter la crème. le sorbitol. le sirop de glucose. la vanille. le beurre de cacao à 30/32°C.\r\nLaisser tourner 1 à 2\'\r\nCadrer entre 30/32° maxi. filmer\r\nPlacer à 17°C.\r\n\r\nWarm the cream at 30 °C\r\nIn the cutter. place the white chocolate at 32/34 °C\r\nAdd the cream. sorbitol. glucose syrup. vanilla. cocoa butter at 30/32 ° C.\r\nLet it run 1 to 2 \'\r\nFrame between 30/32 ° max. \r\nCover with plastic wrap and\r\nPlace at 17 ° C.', 'Warm the cream to 30°C. In the food processor, add the melted ivory chocolate at 32/34°C and add the cream, sorbitol, glucose , melted cocoa butter at 30/32°C and vanilla Blend for 1 to 2 minutes until smooth. Pour in a prepared frame at 30/32°C maximum. Cover with a film and set at 17°C', '', 7, 2.935, NULL, 0, 1, 0, 'reel', '2020-04-03 01:08:58', 0, 0, 0, 1, 15.96, 0.0381, '350', 3, 115, '0', 1, '71', '0.71', 115),
